If you do that now,

580
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:52,624
wouldn't the media
come up with wild speculations?

581
00:45:52,708 --> 00:45:54,960
Rumors about your health,
conflict within the Blue House,

582
00:45:55,043 --> 00:45:56,712
the Blue House playing a power game...

583
00:45:56,795 --> 00:45:59,298
There will be various rumors.
Please help me out here.

584
00:45:59,381 --> 00:46:00,507
Mr. Kim.

585
00:46:02,426 --> 00:46:03,677
I need time...

586
00:46:04,636 --> 00:46:05,637
to verify the candidates.

587
00:46:06,638 --> 00:46:07,514
I'll leave...

588
00:46:09,266 --> 00:46:10,309
the media up to you.

589
00:46:14,438 --> 00:46:17,524
Do you plan to withdraw

590
00:46:18,192 --> 00:46:19,610
Assemblyman Oh's nomination?

591
00:46:21,862 --> 00:46:24,698
You can't do that, sir.

592
00:46:25,282 --> 00:46:26,742
Assemblyman Oh

593
00:46:27,201 --> 00:46:29,578
is a symbolic member
of the nonparty cabinet.

594
00:46:30,162 --> 00:46:31,538
Withdrawing for any reason,

595
00:46:31,622 --> 00:46:34,875
